      <section class="biography" id="biography">
        <h1 class="label">Biography</h1>
        <div class="govspeak">
<p>James Cleverly MP was appointed as a Parliamentary Under Secretary of State at the Department for Exiting the European Union on 4 April 2019.</p>
</div>
      </section>

      <div class="current-roles" id="current-roles">
          <section class="role_appointment role" id="role_appointment_5343">
            <h1 id="parliamentary-under-secretary-of-state">Parliamentary Under Secretary of State</h1>
            <div class="govspeak">
<p>The Parliamentary Under Secretary of State will support the work of the Department for Exiting the European Union.</p>

<ul>
  <li>Policy Coordination & Delivery</li>
  <li>Contingency Planning</li>
  <li>International Agreements and trade</li>
  <li>Borders</li>
  <li>Secondary legislation</li>
  <li>EU (Withdrawal Agreement) Bill support</li>
</ul>
</div>
